"ZNoise - C++ Noise library" is an open source library under LGPL licence. A convenient tool for procedural generation (terrains,textures,etc). The library contains implementation for various "noise sources" : Perlin,Simplex,FBm,Hybrid multifractal, all available from 1 to 4 dimensions. The library is currently under development, feel free to help by signaling issues or forking the project and adding functionnalities.